    <description>MWD26 admin demo — PLACEHOLDER callout subflow. Keeps a stable input/output contract so the Screen Flow deploys. Open this in Flow Builder and replace the placeholder assignment with a native HTTP Callout action (POST callout:Target_Org_NC/services/apexrest/mwd26/requests) that maps the in_* inputs to the request body and sets the out_* outputs from the response. See manual-setup/ADMIN_FLOW_SETUP.md.</description>
